<plot>This is the story of three Italian drag kings. Ivona, Julia and Sonia, are three lesbians who like to perform on stage dressed like men. This documentary is about their lives, their dreams and their loves. And they don't want to change sex, because then the game would end. The big game, the little game, the game of the switch. Each one of the girls built a male character who became their secret friend; the aggressive Julius Kaiser, the gentle Ivan, the bittersweet Jury. Penis is power, says Julia, and the game is about how, as a lesbian, you deal with this reality.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?568509</url></doc>
